---
title: Creamy Chipotle Chicken Soup with black beans and homemade tortilla chips
description: A warming bowl of chicken soup is just what the longer evenings call for. This particular dish is kicked up a notch with the addition of spicy chipotle paste, homemade crunchy tortilla chips, and lashings of cooling creme fraiche.
